Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.93,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.14,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.04,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God! She's really coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.21,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I-I need to calm-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:56.69,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:02:00.56,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You are to be in charge of \Nour next customer, Nako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:01.23,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.00,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to give Nako \Nsuch a difficult task?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.70,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling she'll like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.67,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better to have Ohana,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone related to \Nher, be her attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.90,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.65,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you taking \Nthe position yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.00,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:21.55,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I might attempt to slap \Nher if I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:27.82,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why did Ohana have \Nto go and bring an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:32.54,Default,Den,0000,0000,0000,,She's an important customer \NOhana is bringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:35.54,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.57,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the circumstances, \Nshe's still a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.10,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,The Kissuiso will operate as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.35,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't know how I'm \Ngoing to react to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.51,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.60,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.27,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the ride, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.01,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.50,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's gotten a \Nlot older and trashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:09.91,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed either, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.53,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you've gotten \Na lot older and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.88,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god! The young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.79,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.56,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You've put on some weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.25,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Allow me to escort you \Nto your room, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Beanman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.16,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.55,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,So that's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.57,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.42,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.32,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 13\NShijima's Girl\N(Broken Heart MIX)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So the yukata design \Nhasn't changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There are places nowadays where they \Nlet customers pick from a few designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:02.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's important to \Nhave things like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.19,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.54,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can improve this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.73,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Like, for example, these snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.82,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This area is known for its Yuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.72,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Serving a yuzu-flavored \Nsnack would create
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a topic of discussion between \Nthe waitress and the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.70,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to speak to myself a lot, \Nbecause of what I do for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.88,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.75,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.74,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.50,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You have such pretty eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.76,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, will you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.65,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:50.12,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how scary \Nshe is, Ms. Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:55.39,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She made me do all of her \Nsummer vacation homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.65,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,and took my New Year's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.09,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains why you like Takako,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone with a similar personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.49,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,How was she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.75,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,She's a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.44,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,She gave me so much advice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on how to make this inn better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.90,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.24,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,About yukatas and the tea snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.01,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.43,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.30,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not writing them down because \Nit's what my sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.23,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's as an opinion of a cust-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.02,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.21,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're so hardworking, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.86,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,You just returned and are already back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Just returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:49.59,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:03.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So suddenly, to my regular self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The me that was holding \Nplacards in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and the me who was having \Ndinner with Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,They're not my regular self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The me who works here has \Nbecome my regular self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, waitress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I want to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary to climb a \Nhill with heels on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to \Ndo if something happens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a customer after ignoring her plea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.46,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There really is nothing \Nhere, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.96,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But there's this thing called a \NBonbori Festival around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing I \Nliked about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They say your wish comes \Ntrue, and I believed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Since forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask the gods to restore
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your relationship with Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:06.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I guess correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:06.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} get dumped by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Got dumped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many other boys out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little short and thick,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but since you're my daughter-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't suddenly start \Nacting like a mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:36.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this inn because \Nyou speak so highly of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to be depressed because \Nyou got dumped by some guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better show me what's \Nso great about this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.61,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I guess her situation with him \Nis worse than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"It's no time to be depressed because \Nyou got dumped by some guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Dumped by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Dumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it means to be dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.39,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.18,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, I need you to make the dashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.20,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Being this time of the year,\Nare you cooking smelt-whiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.10,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:46.64,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,You might laugh, saying that \Nit's "plain boring," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Predicting is the same thing as hoping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.84,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to kill \Nmy hopes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.76,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you should
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be trying to surprise \Nme in a different way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.33,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,like preparing several kinds of salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.96,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been a lot easier if
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she had just called it "boring."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.27,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been had as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.78,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,The bath isn't ready yet-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, this inn is as strict as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.52,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to randomize \Ncleaning times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,based on watching the customers' activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The good thing about a hot \Nspring inn is being able
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to enter the hot spring \Nwhenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.54,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,She got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.17,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,The nape of her neck was so sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.30,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.93,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,She's a troubling customer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.41,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But I still think she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.18,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what she said about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cooking wasn't wrong either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.90,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.37,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely better than that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako that the young \Nmaster always brings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.06,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako says she'll be on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:54.40,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.26,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.93,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to handle my sister-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.86,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to rely on an outsider \Neven during a situation like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.20,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't only the Kissuiso's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.78,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,This is our problem! The Shijima's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.18,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Though she's my daughter, \Nshe's still a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:30.15,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I didn't \Ntake charge of her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.72,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,If my personal feelings get in the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.56,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if the \Ndaughter of the Mikasa family were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always prepare two bath towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.99,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What about for the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.81,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She likes very hot tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd raise the temperature \Nof the water in the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.38,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.23,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,For people visiting for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to find out \Nabout their preferences,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.11,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure to use it for reference
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the next time they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:06.43,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,But, though that customer is \Nvisiting for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.95,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,she actually isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:13.02,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You and I know a lot \Nabout that customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.06,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,They're a lot similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.04,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That customer and the \NMadam Manager, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.38,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.73,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.79,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,They're different kinds of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.36,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,but they have their similarities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that they're \Nmother and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.20,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You're praising that \Ncustomer too much there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.10,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude, even for the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager to take part \Nin the kitchen's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:51.65,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,However, do you mind letting me \Nuse it just this once, Mr. Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.20,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.95,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind letting me prepare the futon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the customer in the Wisteria Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.36,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.20,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.13,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.58,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You're back to your regular old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.84,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,My regular old self...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.22,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.39,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of effort has been put into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:42.99,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special dish for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:48.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Stewed fish cake is pretty \Nplain for a dish at an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:49.71,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.07,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.96,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Serving my favorite food like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using the bath, Beanman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mind getting out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.68,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.01,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,A customer will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.44,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be cleaning despite
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether you decide to \Nuse the bath or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,B-But-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.57,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wash yourself in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, be that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Those sheets aren't dry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you can't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're not hugging rolled-up sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Then I need you to be its \Nreplacement tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please ask your boyfriend instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something a daughter \Nshould be saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:58.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're more of a "woman" \Nthan a "mother" to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.82,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be better to \Nwake her up three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:11.95,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.02,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a morning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.08,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She tosses about in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.13,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.71,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,In this area, it's cool at \Nnight even during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.78,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Serving hot rice porridge in the \Nmorning might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:22.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.47,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe we should serve some \Nvegetable juice with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the most
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spoken with the \NMadam Manager by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And it's about Mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:38.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam Manager is my grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:42.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and obviously, Mom's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:48.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mom-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The customer in the Wisteria Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Could you bring me some sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Warm, not hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and three cans of beer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Soft drinks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.92,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and a geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,G-Geisha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at this hour, we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Then in that case, an old lady \Nand a young girl will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.14,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come in and have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.46,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but we still \Nhave work to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.69,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Have a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.33,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,She got drunk over soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's really good at getting \Nthe wrong idea, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:58.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that Ko was important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.31,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you tell him so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized I like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I got rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.15,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.71,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,A woman from the Shijima family
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,giving up after being \Nrejected once or twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:19.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you fought \Nhard for Dad, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.29,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.14,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,He was strait-laced,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.54,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,so I was rejected four times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.56,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The fifth time's the charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:41.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to keep him at \Nmy beck and call anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko already has a life of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, do you want \Nto come back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:52.30,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You can enter his life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I already have my life, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A life at the Kissuiso! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd rather put work over love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.16,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She really is a woman \Nof the Shijima family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.89,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I got told.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's also festing it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Both Mom and Grandma are festing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:22.91,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fes-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.81,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I also need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, having their kid \Nrecognize their effort
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,signals the end of a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.60,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,She's not listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you can hold your drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Another shot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.65,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.60,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do I {\i1}look{\i0} like I'm working overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.47,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.70,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.27,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Miss Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.52,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Her, Mom, and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:12.95,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.61,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I ride a motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.23,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember you being this weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.19,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.31,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:48.46,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You succeeded the inn, and \NOhana was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,And then you always make \Nme do stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.33,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:06.16,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty light, aren't you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.72,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make her worry too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.84,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:23.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to be that \Nmother I always hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.53,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If you really start hating \Nyour job, you can come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden acting \Nlike a mother again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you need to let \Nme act cool at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Beanman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.38,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.78,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.85,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's it say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.15,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.29,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:22.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Calling it "retro" would be too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:26.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,However, without change, things \Nwould be too sedimented.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:30.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's very difficult to get \Nthrough to your customer that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your inn isn't going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:35.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The Kissuiso is always evolving,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,in order to continue its \Nservice that is unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect its \N"retro" tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can really tell that \Nthe staff have spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:47.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very warm inn that \NI enjoyed staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.26,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.94,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It was praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.35,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.89,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.68,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Beanman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.59,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:16.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something \Nafter Mom came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:22.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Though I miss Ko,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:26.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I never feel the urge \Nto go back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm not returning \Nto Tokyo because things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't the same between Ko and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:35.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's because this place is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:40.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I chose this place to be my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I love the Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:47.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I love everyone who works here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I love Grandma, the Madam Manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also love my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.32,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for everything I've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:07.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:10.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:14.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:22.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.79,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I even brought my swimsuit \NI wear during competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:43.79,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to ask her out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.89,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become a waitress, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:49.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand you, Yuina.
